      "intro_html": "Answers about ordering, care supplies and delivery. Learn more about {{ link }} and free care consumables in our categories.",
      "intro_link_label": "incontinence care",
      "faq_1_q": "How does prescription billing work for incontinence products?",
      "faq_1_a": "<p>On request we handle <strong>billing with your health insurer</strong>. You order suitable products from us; we check the details and manage the formal process so you can skip the pharmacy visit.</p>",
      "faq_2_q": "How does home delivery work?",
      "faq_2_a": "<p>After your order and verification we pack items <strong>discreetly and securely</strong> and ship to your chosen address. Delivery time and shipping details are shown during checkout and in your confirmation.</p>",
      "faq_3_q": "Do I still need to go to the pharmacy?",
      "faq_3_a": "<p>No. With prescription billing or a free care box, we deliver <strong>directly to your home</strong>, saving time and making regular supply easier.</p>",
      "faq_4_q": "How are products selected and reviewed?",
      "faq_4_a": "<p>Our range is guided by <strong>professional care experience</strong>. We focus on reliable quality, appropriate sizes and a clear assortment so you can find a suitable solution quickly.</p>",
      "faq_5_q": "I am unsure which products to choose — who can help?",
      "faq_5_a": "<p>Our customer service can help with <strong>sizes, quantities and the order process</strong>. For medical decisions, please also consult your doctor or care professional.</p>",
      "faq_6_q": "How do reorders work for ongoing supply?",
      "faq_6_a": "<p>You can <strong>reorder previous items easily</strong>. With an approved care box or ongoing prescription supply, delivery usually continues automatically after approval.</p>"
