  "pflegeboxi": {
    "launcher_aria": "Open help and FAQ — Pflegeboxi",
    "bubble": "Hi, I’m Pflegeboxi. Tap me — I’ll be happy to help!",
    "title": "Quick answers",
    "close": "Close",
    "dismiss_launcher": "Hide Pflegeboxi",
    "mascot_alt": "Pflegeboxi mascot",
    "more_help": "More help",
    "faq_1_q": "How does shipping work?",
    "faq_1_a": "After payment is confirmed, we pack your order securely and hand it to our carrier. Delivery time and cost are shown in the cart and on the shipping page.",
    "faq_2_q": "Can I return something?",
    "faq_2_a": "You can return unused items within the statutory withdrawal period. You’ll find details in our terms and the cancellation policy.",
    "faq_3_q": "Which payment methods do you offer?",
    "faq_3_a": "At checkout you can choose from the payment options we display — cards, PayPal, and others depending on our integration.",
    "faq_4_q": "How do I reach customer service?",
    "faq_4_a": "Use the contact page or the details in the legal notice. We’ll get back to you as soon as we can.",
    "faq_5_q": "Do you ship internationally?",
    "faq_5_a": "Where we ship is explained in our shipping or delivery policy. At checkout you’ll see options for your address.",
    "faq_6_q": "How secure is shopping here?",
    "faq_6_a": "Checkout uses encrypted connections. Payments are processed by established payment providers — we don’t store your full card details on our servers.",
    "faq_7_q": "Will I get an order confirmation?",
    "faq_7_a": "Yes — you should receive an email with the key details. If you don’t see it, check your spam folder.",
    "faq_8_q": "My parcel arrived damaged — what now?",
    "faq_8_a": "Take photos of the packaging and contents and contact support promptly. That helps us arrange a replacement or clarify things with the carrier.",
    "faq_9_q": "Do you offer discounts for larger quantities?",
    "faq_9_a": "Current promotions or tiered pricing appear on the site or product page. For bulk needs, a quick message to support can help.",
    "faq_10_q": "How fast is delivery?",
    "faq_10_a": "It depends on the product and shipping method. You’ll see estimated timing on the product page, in the cart, and in your confirmation email.",
    "faq_11_q": "Are all items always in stock?",
    "faq_11_a": "Unless noted otherwise, items should be available. If there’s a delay or restock, we’ll reflect that in your order or via support.",
    "faq_12_q": "What does “currently unavailable” mean?",
    "faq_12_a": "The item can’t be ordered for now — restocking or sold out. Use a notify-me option if available, or check back later.",
    "faq_13_q": "Can I add a gift note?",
    "faq_13_a": "If the theme or checkout offers a gift or message field, use that. Otherwise ask support before placing the order.",
    "faq_14_q": "How does the right of withdrawal work?",
    "faq_14_a": "You generally have a statutory period after receiving the goods (exceptions may apply — e.g. sealed hygiene products). Exact steps are in our cancellation policy.",
    "faq_15_q": "Where are terms and privacy policy?",
    "faq_15_a": "Links are usually in the site footer — terms, cancellation policy, and privacy. You can also search within the shop domain.",
    "faq_16_q": "What data do you store about me?",
    "faq_16_a": "Only what’s needed for the contract, shipping, and legal obligations — explained in detail in the privacy policy.",
    "faq_17_q": "Can I order as a business with a VAT ID?",
    "faq_17_a": "If checkout offers VAT ID or company fields, use them. Otherwise support can help with correct invoicing.",
    "faq_18_q": "Any notes on best-before dates or hygiene items?",
    "faq_18_a": "Where relevant, you’ll see shelf-life info and any special return rules on the product page. Ask before purchase if unsure.",
    "faq_19_q": "Do you ship bulky or heavy parcels?",
    "faq_19_a": "Large or heavy shipments may use freight or extra fees — look for shipping notes in the cart or at checkout.",
    "faq_20_q": "I’m unsure which product to choose — what should I do?",
    "faq_20_a": "Compare sizes, pack quantities, and usage notes in the description. For medical or personal needs, also speak with a qualified professional — we don’t replace medical advice."
  },
